  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Language Immersion:</strong> Newcomer is a language immersion experience for beginners to<strong> </strong>learn and practice 9 languages:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Latin-American Spanish</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>French</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Italian</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>German</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Castilian Spanish</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Brazilian Portuguese</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Turkish</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dutch</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tagalog</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Results:</strong> In your adventure, you will:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >learn and communicate fundamental survival phrases with a variety of in-game NPCs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >gain exposure to thousands of new words </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >start to identify correct pronunciation </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >learn beginner vocabulary</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >encounter grammar naturally</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a Newcomer, you are given a <u>phrasebook</u> and a quest...  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/a40fee9bd17f16c9c2a239039bcf6555.poster.avif?t=1766420685\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/a40fee9bd17f16c9c2a239039bcf6555.webm?t=1766420685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/a40fee9bd17f16c9c2a239039bcf6555.mp4?t=1766420685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You encounter target language speakers and <u>start to communicate</u> using basic phrases... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/a62efdd294be21889fbb660fc6e70242.poster.avif?t=1766420685\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/a62efdd294be21889fbb660fc6e70242.webm?t=1766420685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/a62efdd294be21889fbb660fc6e70242.mp4?t=1766420685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your ability to <u>translate</u> your target language makes it possible to understand your new language... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/8a8772db6e3acc1686f27f1b2c89b3ba.poster.avif?t=1766420685\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/8a8772db6e3acc1686f27f1b2c89b3ba.webm?t=1766420685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/8a8772db6e3acc1686f27f1b2c89b3ba.mp4?t=1766420685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you travel through new areas, you <u>review vocabulary by battling</u> hostile creatures... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/a7206895ab8bac81f381761a1e360099.poster.avif?t=1766420685\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/a7206895ab8bac81f381761a1e360099.webm?t=1766420685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/a7206895ab8bac81f381761a1e360099.mp4?t=1766420685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You start using your new language to <u>complete conversation tasks</u> by discussing a variety of people, places, and things within the world... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/3ef55421fd3f7be9444d0c9d087681a9.poster.avif?t=1766420685\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/3ef55421fd3f7be9444d0c9d087681a9.webm?t=1766420685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/3ef55421fd3f7be9444d0c9d087681a9.mp4?t=1766420685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You level up and <u>unlock new words and phrases</u>, enabling you to engage in deeper and more nuanced conversations... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/ac568441648fe700e31fd28cb25f8479.poster.avif?t=1766420685\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/ac568441648fe700e31fd28cb25f8479.webm?t=1766420685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/ac568441648fe700e31fd28cb25f8479.mp4?t=1766420685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You start to utilize <u>intelligent translations</u> which explain individual words in more detail... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/04bd2842d5991dcb83db76ad0f59ea81.poster.avif?t=1766420685\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/04bd2842d5991dcb83db76ad0f59ea81.webm?t=1766420685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your new language takes you to many parts of the <u>open world</u>... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/08e2b1476362878f3d8ec007e883bd72.poster.avif?t=1766420685\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/08e2b1476362878f3d8ec007e883bd72.webm?t=1766420685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/08e2b1476362878f3d8ec007e883bd72.mp4?t=1766420685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ultimately, you must learn your second language to <u>defeat the Dark Crimson</u>... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/2afb6b34d082c07e4cbfb399bff5d4fb.poster.avif?t=1766420685\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/2afb6b34d082c07e4cbfb399bff5d4fb.webm?t=1766420685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/2afb6b34d082c07e4cbfb399bff5d4fb.mp4?t=1766420685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play and learn many languages... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/4b4d3ce123d7a70c0e94f1da6fdcfb26.gif?t=1766420685\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/4b4d3ce123d7a70c0e94f1da6fdcfb26.poster.avif?t=1766420685\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p>",
